Barcelona fans have had to deal with their pains after the Spanish football club crashed out of the Champions League in a what most described as a shocking exit. Kostas Manolas had sent Roma through to the semi-finals on Tuesday after an incredible 3-0 victory over Barcelona saw the Italian side overhaul a 4-1 first-leg deficit and advance on away goals. However, Barcelona fans seemed not to have come into reality with the outcome of the match as supporters from rivalry clubs took to Twitter on Wednesday to mock the La Liga title hopefuls. See hilarious reactions below:       